            "heading": undefined,
            "content": "Arch's consensus is powered by Arch's native token using a dPoS model for block production and threshold key distribution. The network state and activity is propagated across nodes via the GossipSub protocol, ensuring that all validators receive updates in a decentralized and fault-tolerant manner. Leveraging FROST + ROAST, Arch comes to consensus on new user-submitted Bitcoin UTXOs and settles them directly on Bitcoin with our cryptographic multi-sig architecture."
