            "content": "The final stage involves block formation, where the leader assembles a comprehensive block structure that serves as an immutable record in the blockchain. This structure contains several essential components: a reference to the previous block to maintain chain continuity, a precise timestamp documenting when the block was created, and a list of transaction IDs that were included in the block."
